{"tid":587841,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"再次證明攝影師玩死攝影業","createTime":"2018-03-10T17:28:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-11T10:43:17.000Z","uid":11779,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"54662d985b9688e13e080f85361ab81b7797ca2f","tid":587841,"uid":11779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T17:28:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/11/012523_fba8ee49f993ffae3cf4927eca6547d5.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F11%2F012523_fba8ee49f993ffae3cf4927eca6547d5.jpeg&h=5538e98a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/11/012526_ef79609f378b5c9f3928378f18ec61cb.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F11%2F012526_ef79609f378b5c9f3928378f18ec61cb.jpeg&h=cf48cc22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/11/012527_0e334e07f6f4df6da2842acf258c7701.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F11%2F012527_0e334e07f6f4df6da2842acf258c7701.jpeg&h=7b946cb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n收得平又老土都算，啲構圖同chopping想點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 放啲咁嘅相上FB比人睇，對攝影業打擊好大ga。"},{"pid":"d5a7730068b555396b2834e564991e063a8988ab","tid":587841,"uid":174074,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T17:42:22.000Z","msg":"不如去snap<br />\n仲可以自己影"},{"pid":"abd24a98398a08daed43c290c147eb840eee54cd","tid":587841,"uid":81575,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T17:45:46.000Z","msg":"有差嘅攝影師，先至托得出價錢貴而影得好嗰批，你要多謝佢地<br />\n若然佢咁既質素都多生意過影得好嗰批攝影師，要反省嘅反而係影得好嗰批"},{"pid":"59f10a0155e7174d5e8566c27936a1d113bb31cc","tid":587841,"uid":79546,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T18:27:40.000Z","msg":"平有平做<br />\n貴有貴做<br />\n冇人墊底<br />\n香港人又會嫌你貴"},{"pid":"ed8c99a5b0209e4c75b36b902fb67eb20418b818","tid":587841,"uid":97827,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T19:03:39.000Z","msg":"一分錢一分貨 明嘅都明<br />\n你係有料既收十萬一緝都有人搵你<br />\n結論:自己有料就唔洗驚比人搶客/壓低個價 而唔係放上嚟鳩叫"},{"pid":"6919ccca54e5b6c70a87780974765241c9ab59e4","tid":587841,"uid":11779,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T02:21:47.000Z","msg":"太多買部機就學人接生意嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bd8b20ab9ab0d17bf395a5fb719ec8f7ff7d2b5","tid":587841,"uid":135896,"like":8,"dislike":5,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T02:46:17.000Z","msg":"做生意嘅嘢，最緊要唔係技術，系要明白市場嘅需求<br />\n<br />\n唔通你想收佢哋＄3-4000日出時分拖晒成家想去鳳凰山影文青style家庭相咩？普通人想影家庭相真係想要啲咁嘅嘢？<br />\n<br />\n香港做生意最易攪就係人流，一開始一定係引人黎做旺個場，做得好一個帶一個介紹黎，一日有幾單1000幾百家庭相，一個月營業額都有10幾萬"},{"pid":"2304da5713a3d331526c4b0c3bc84a122d0c4534","tid":587841,"uid":117628,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T04:35:04.000Z","msg":"不如&quot;專業攝影師&quot; 講下點樣揀一個好既攝影師??"},{"pid":"3ca1ed72710bd9f9cfdc520dcd072b1b8f4cc6fb","tid":587841,"uid":130901,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T04:38:56.000Z","msg":"有樓主咁高要求既自然無人玩呢廉價攝影，百貨應百客，自命清高窮一世<br />\n<br />\n而且攝影唔係國防科技，器材越黎越平係事實"},{"pid":"c22a4d7caec59a49ed451400c232960eee00e8d1","tid":587841,"uid":11779,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T05:27:58.000Z","msg":"竟然有人覺得影得靚，希望你地第時搵佢影 但影完唔好話中伏。"},{"pid":"88652b8a70cb61b9af7150f968c98ea1fc958684","tid":587841,"uid":54371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T05:30:57.000Z","msg":"同自拍館差唔多質素<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9bb703ca4b2ff4b99d292b12ab78ecece93a38d","tid":587841,"uid":50899,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T06:34:35.000Z","msg":"我想問下呢d 咁主觀既野，你憑咩話人唔得？<br />\n<br />\n靚唔靚有對與錯架？<br />\n<br />\n你唔去美術館大叫錯錯錯！ 全部都錯晒？"},{"pid":"69ae5776e02daffab0c4f17653cba73e4b66b668","tid":587841,"uid":50899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T06:35:05.000Z","msg":"雖然我唔會幫襯佢地"},{"pid":"2363ab8b005e6df05c7564ac44a8260a13060851","tid":587841,"uid":42246,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T06:36:59.000Z","msg":"基層市場哈洗理？<br />\n窮人唔比搵攝影記師<br />\n<br />\n屌你冇腦樓豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"445609a9d11385b445e65bf7c170744093e8e3db","tid":587841,"uid":44377,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T06:42:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>竟然有人覺得影得靚，希望你地第時搵佢影 但影完唔好話中伏。</blockquote><br />\n又老老實實，你見到d sample咁樣，你仲搵佢影既話就唔叫中伏啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0539297132dabe86b32d0edbf0f71c541c5a7c99","tid":587841,"uid":55,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T07:00:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5f534beee6783af92b803f88ffdedfa4ca63361b","tid":587841,"uid":188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T07:05:00.000Z","msg":"你情我願 有乜所謂 <br />\n你值呢個價自然有人比 自己抬價都無用 唔好怪市場"},{"pid":"d8b0be3b4bdd8a5a984f8e56dccdb0c29322ab86","tid":587841,"uid":55374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T07:10:03.000Z","msg":"幾百蚊你想比啲咩你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcc97ad17110ae337f64e89223ee1beffb70d97e","tid":587841,"uid":81756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T09:55:03.000Z","msg":"19影樓加個backdrop仲想點 玩埋vr<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d88a66bcc4bdffca9cb30e1be0323247dfe0186","tid":587841,"uid":175752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T09:57:30.000Z","msg":"而家d港豬 有景深就以為專業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b31556e26918117d8454874396e150d72973b094","tid":587841,"uid":40812,